    "Exploratory edges never satisfy academic-plausibility eligibility (PRD 026 §7 stage 3); they exist for reflection breadth and path display.",
    "credential_levels: bachelor only in v1.",
    "Edge explanations are load-bearing user-facing copy: the UI's 'why is this school here?' chain cites the edge explanation for the concept-to-program hop (PRD 026 §5, §9)."
